programme.desc: Can the team pull off their biggest challenge to date and make Nerys McGarry - who has lost eight stone - 21 years younger?

programme.title: 10 Years Younger USA: From Mother Hen To Red Hot Mama
programme.desc: Karen is a mother hen whose chicks have flown the coop. To spice up the future she'll share with her husband, the 10 YEARS YOUNGER team will revamp her appearance – and make her feel beautiful and sexy for the first time in years!
programme.sub-title: From Mother Hen To Red Hot Mama

programme.title: 10 Years Younger USA: The Same Girl I Used To Be
programme.desc: Renee is a brassy landscape designer whose looks need a redesign. She needs a professional, feminine style – and she needs it in time for her upcoming class reunion. Now, it's up to 10 YEARS YOUNGER to beat the clock and give her a hot new look.
programme.sub-title: The Same Girl I Used To Be

programme.title: 10 Years Younger USA: All Boys to All Glamour
programme.desc: Patty is a busy mom, shuttling the kids to school and basketball games. In a house with three boys, a husband and even a male dog, Patty's girl-time gets lost in the shuffle. The Glam Squad and our doctors are going to give Patty some time for herself.

programme.title: 10 Years Younger UK: Debbie Rotchell
programme.desc: Essex girl Debbie Rotchell, 49, smokes 15,000 cigarettes a year and loves to sunbathe. Debbie gets a wake-up call when a poll of one hundred people puts her at 55. Just as well Nicky Hambleton-Jones is on hand with her time-fighting trio.

programme.title: 10 Years Younger USA: Scrubs No More
programme.desc: Darcey spends her days caring for three kids and her nights working as a nurse, with no time left for herself. Experts perform the latest procedures in dermatology and dentistry, and the glam squad takes her from scrubs to sass.

programme.title: 10 Years Younger USA: It’s Like Pulling Teeth
programme.desc: Daniel Trnka is a man in constant pain. A rare hereditary defect has left his teeth crumbling and destroyed. Now, with a new younger bride, and baby daughter, Daniel wants to look his age before people mistake him for his daughter's grandfather.

programme.title: 10 Years Younger USA: Looks To Inspire
programme.desc: Becky trains and inspires foster parents, but also wants looks that inspire. So, our doctors will lift her face and brighten her smile. Next, the Glam Squad will polish up her wardrobe, hair and makeup – all to make Becky look 10 YEARS YOUNGER.

programme.title: 10 Years Younger USA: The Competitive Edge
programme.desc: As a teen, Luray used to go from the beach to a tanning booth. Now she's after a corporate career, and doesn't want to look like an old lady compared to the other job candidates.

programme.title: Wild At Heart: Episode 3
programme.desc: Leopard's Den is looking after a sick and orphaned baby elephant called Togo. However, despite Evan and Du Plessis' constant vigil, Togo is dying from a broken heart. Evan is distraught and Du Plessis promises they will look after her together.

programme.title: Wild At Heart: Episode 4
programme.desc: Sarah's absence couldn't have come at a worse time for Leopard's Den. Nature Conservation is carrying out their annual inspection and everything has to be tip top. Danny's determined they pass with flying colours and everyone is roped in to help.

programme.title: Wild At Heart: Episode 5
programme.desc: Everyone's excited at the prospect of Leopard's Den's new arrival. Bash, Danny's old tutor and Rosie's Godfather, is coming from England to help Danny grow his veterinary practice.

programme.title: Wild At Heart: Episode 6
programme.desc: The Trevanions are delighted when Fatani asks Danny to take an aggressive hippo off his hands. As they prepare for its arrival Sarah gets a bit of a shock when her mother Caroline beats the hippo to the post.

programme.title: Wild At Heart: Episode 7
programme.desc: Business is looking up at Leopard's Den but Sarah is feeling agitated. Caroline thinks it because Simon, her ex husband and Evan and Olivia's Dad, is arriving from England to get married. But Sarah has other things on her mind.

programme.title: Wild At Heart: Episode 8
programme.desc: Danny is undertaking a drugs trial at Leopard's Den. But de-worming wildebeest isn't Caroline's idea of fun. She hates animals and finds the whole business mind-numbingly boring.

programme.title: Wild At Heart: Episode 9
programme.desc: Du Plessis is in a foul mood. It's his 60th birthday and he has no intentions of celebrating it. But the Trevanions have other ideas and Caroline is organising a surprise party.

programme.title: Wild At Heart: Episode 10
programme.desc: All is quiet at Leopard's Den as Sarah, Evan and Olivia gather at the hospital. Danny has been given the all clear to go home. But Du Plessis is still unconscious and seriously ill. Caroline keeps a tender vigil at his bedside.

programme.title: Tearaway Teen To Beauty Queen: Episode 3
programme.desc: Behaving like a beauty queen proves a tough challenge for the 7 remaining tearaway teens. Mentor Michelle Fryatt expects grace both on and off the catwalk, but shocking bullying and bitching leads to the most explosive elimination yet.

programme.title: Tearaway Teen To Beauty Queen: Episode 4
programme.desc: The 6 remaining wannabe beauty queens face their toughest challenge yet – a full-blown pageant in Manchester. But with stress and stage fright causing explosive outbursts and tearful meltdowns, which three can Michelle risk taking to America as finalists?

programme.title: Tearaway Teen To Beauty Queen: Episode 5
programme.desc: Beauty queen Michelle Fryatt challenges the three remaining teens to survive the media spot light as celebrities – but she didn't mean late night parties and boozing. So will bad behaviour play a part at the elimination in Chicago?

programme.title: Tearaway Teen To Beauty Queen: Episode 6
programme.desc: Beauty Queen Michelle decides which teen deserves to be Miss Teen England. But can her chosen tearaway conquer the US teen professionals and bring home the crown for England at the pageant? Prepare for tears and tantrums...

programme.title: The Embassy: Episode 1
programme.desc: Thailand is in a state of political unrest and 41-year-old David, a musician from New South Wales, has just been arrested for overstaying his visa. Can the embassy get him out?

programme.title: The Embassy: Episode 2
programme.desc: The embassy is called to a young couple in crisis. Their 7 month-old baby girl, Laney, has died from a virus and they need to get her home to Australia. But can they get baby Laney on the plane?

programme.title: The Embassy: Episode 3
programme.desc: The embassy is on high alert after a wealthy Australian banker goes missing. Is he alive? Holed up in a bar somewhere? Or does he not want to be found?

programme.title: The Embassy: Episode 4
programme.desc: Jarryd's been busted for drugs in a country where they still have the death penalty. And now he plans to double-cross the Thai authorities and escape to Singapore with his pregnant girlfriend.

programme.title: The Embassy: Episode 5
programme.desc: Beau was left for dead by the side of a road after a horrific motorbike crash. Now he wants to discharge himself from hospital. Can the embassy stop him before he self-destructs?

programme.title: The Embassy: Episode 6
programme.desc: The embassy visits a convicted drug dealer in the world's most notorious prison. But Steven claims he's the innocent victim of an undercover drug sting gone wrong.

programme.title: The Embassy: Episode 7

programme.title: Tests, Trends & Action: Ford / Volvo / Suzuki

programme.title: Tests, Trends & Action: Volkswagen

programme.title: Tuning: Alpina / Mercedes

programme.title: Tuning: BMW / Chevrolet / Audi

programme.title: Tuning: Dodge / Mini Cooper / Porsche

programme.title: Tuning: Lamborghini / Porsche / Jaguar

programme.title: Classic: Alfa Romeo / Apollo 3500 GT

programme.title: Classic: AMC Pacer / Arabella Classics

programme.title: Classic: Auto Union Type C in Monte Carlo / Bangkok Classic Car Ride / Bayer K 67 research vehicle

programme.sub-title: Auto Union Type C in Monte Carlo / Bangkok Classic Car Ride / Bayer K 67 research vehicle

programme.title: Classic: Bentley / Borgward Isabella Cabriolet

programme.title: Classic: BMW

programme.title: Classic: Bugatti / Chevrolet Corvair / Chrysler Airflow

programme.title: Classic: Citroën 2CV / Concorso d'Eleganza am Comer See / Studebaker Avanti
